ics rather than, for example, a recipe:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let instructions = \"\"\"","    Suggest related topics. Keep them concise (three to seven words) and make sure they \\","    build naturally from the person's topic.","    \"\"\"","","let session = LanguageModelSession(instructions: instructions)","","let prompt = \"Making homemade bread\"","let response = try await session.respond(to: prompt)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Apple trains the model to obey instructions over any commands it receives in prompts,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"so don’t include untrusted content in instructions. For more on how instructions","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"impact generation quality and safety, see ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc://com.apple.foundationmodels/documentation/FoundationModels/improving-the-safety-of-generative-model-output","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All input to the model contributes tokens to the context window of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc://com.apple.foundationmodels/documentation/FoundationModels/LanguageModelSession"},{"text":" — including the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc://com.apple.foundationmodels/documentation/FoundationModels/Instructions","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc://com.apple.foundationmodels/documentation/FoundationModels/Prompt","isActive":true},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc://com.apple.foundationmodels/documentation/FoundationModels/Tool","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc://com.apple.foundationmodels/documentation/FoundationModels/Generable","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" types, and the model’s responses. If your session exceeds the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"available context size, it throws"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.foundationmodels/documentation/FoundationModels/LanguageModelSession/GenerationError/exceededContextWindowSize(_:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Instructions can consume a lot of tokens that contribute to the context window"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"size. To reduce your instruction size:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Write shorter instructions to save tokens.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Provide only the information necessary to perform the task."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use concise and imperative language instead of indirect or jargon that the model","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"might misinterpret.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Aim for one to three paragraphs instead of including a significant amount of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"background information, policy, or extra content.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For more","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information on managing the context window size, see"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Technotes/tn3193-managing-the-on-device-foundation-model-s-context-window","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Details you provide that define the model’s int